{"tid":231699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：怪叔叔見光死？坐車「遮」到冚","createTime":"2017-05-06T08:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T09:37:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff3d6e6eab2ea9d9dfdfdefa8755ebc114850fd","tid":231699,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170506/photo/bkn-20170506043019201-0506_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170505224829\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170506%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170506043019201-0506_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170505224829&h=21c740cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">男子一直用「遮」把自己遮到冚，行為詭異。 （fb「巴士的事討論區」圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n白天乘坐交通工具，碰上猛烈陽光，有人會用書用手袋或用雨傘等擋去陽光，大家可能都偶有所見，不覺得奇怪。不過近日一名中年男乘客，坐車時用「遮」把自己遮到冚，行為詭異，被網民笑是否做錯事，因而見不得光，一見光即死？ <br />\n<br />\n有網民在facebook群組「巴士的事討論區」發貼，指「第一次見人搭巴士開傘」，講述由深水步乘九巴上車，直到前往天水圍一段路程，都目睹一名中年男子一直保持開傘動作，未有曝光容貌。從數張照片所見，一名穿白色上衣和灰色長褲的男乘客，在車廂下層車尾位置，一直把雨傘呈半開狀態，完全遮蓋自己頭部。<br />\n<br />\n男子行為十分可疑，拍照者和網民無從判斷其真正目的。有人調侃是巴士有鬼，阿叔怕怕。也有人笑謂可能是哪一個上了年紀的明星，用此招來避開騷擾。另有人認為或許是大叔不懂得關掉出口位冷風掣，惟有出此下策。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\nJason Yip：好多人今時今日都唔識搞個冷風出口<br />\n<br />\nKit Mak：唔見得光 一見光就魂飛魄散<br />\n<br />\nApple Lau：人型遮？遮型人？車中人遮！<br />\n<br />\nHenry Yui：鹹魚唔曬得<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170506/bkn-20170506043019201-0506_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170506%2Fbkn-20170506043019201-0506_00822_001.html&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=4b038226\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170506/bkn-20170506043019201-0506_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"511b3a54427e32e366ed7005a1e6f2d0d510f3cd","tid":231699,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"咁都做到新聞"},{"pid":"ad748ed7495c8f28920a42d04679bceb6da034cd","tid":231699,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jlc5tvyf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjlc5tvyf&h=0a56f849&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c134f6382d322c6b60b8ca4acd053ead7c6d8cda","tid":231699,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"我見過佢，第一眼睇到真係比佢嚇左一跳，全程都遮住自己，好鬼奇怪"},{"pid":"4f1127d08d110a84113e88fc9b77836ca2de563d","tid":231699,"uid":27381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"有種病係唔見得陽光"},{"pid":"6c1f686d4f70d4c7b9336070a2f586751e8c4c50","tid":231699,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://banshee.ai-saloon.com/personal/user2936/pic/79706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbanshee.ai-saloon.com%2Fpersonal%2Fuser2936%2Fpic%2F79706.jpg&h=7254e0f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3379889f10c00136e1a70b43b94057d0ae903bb","tid":231699,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:37:52.000Z","msg":"似乎係某種情緒疾患 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}